---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How VideoGenNews collects, uses, and protects visitor information."
  breadcrumbs={[{ name: 'Privacy' }]}
>
  <section class="hero-panel compact">
    <p class="hero-kicker">Privacy</p>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>This policy explains what data VideoGenNews collects and how it is used.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="story-shell">
    <p><strong>Effective date:</strong> February 24, 2026</p>

    <h2>Information we collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Basic technical logs such as IP address, browser, and requested URL.</li>
      <li>Information you provide directly by email or contact forms.</li>
      <li>Newsletter signup details if you subscribe.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How we use information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Operate, secure, and improve the site.</li>
      <li>Respond to editorial, correction, and business requests.</li>
      <li>Measure aggregate traffic and content performance.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Cookies and analytics</h2>
    <p>VideoGenNews may use cookies or similar storage for session behavior, analytics, and performance monitoring.</p>

    <h2>Third-party services</h2>
    <p>Vendors used for hosting, analytics, and email delivery may process limited data on our behalf.</p>

    <h2>Data retention</h2>
    <p>We retain personal data only as long as needed for operational, legal, or security purposes.</p>

    <h2>Your choices</h2>
    <p>You can request access, correction, or deletion of personal data by contacting <a href="mailto:privacy@videogennews.com">privacy@videogennews.com</a>.</p>

    <h2>Policy updates</h2>
    <p>Material changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
